New-Item .gitignore -ItemType File
notepad .gitignore
```

Paste this into Notepad and save:
```
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
*.db
*.sqlite3

# Model files (too large for git)
*.gguf
*.onnx
*.bin
models/

# Node
node_modules/
npm-debug.log

# Environment files (contains API keys)
.env

# ChromaDB
chroma_db/

# Build
build/
dist/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log